{"type":"message","id":"676391d6","parentId":"68cd2b0e","timestamp":"2026-03-15T04:08:30.941Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"  I've read the files. Let me summarize what I found:\n\n1. **SOUL.md** - I am who I am - genuinely helpful, have opinions, be resourceful, earn trust, respect boundaries. Be concise when needed, thorough when it matters. Not corporate, not sycophant - just good.\n\n2. **USER.md** - Empty template, no info about the user yet.\n\n3. **Memory files** - Don't exist yet (it's a fresh workspace)\n\n4. **MEMORY.md** - Doesn't exist yet\n\nSo I'm starting fresh. The user mentioned \"if the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model.\" Looking at the Runtime info:\n- model=haihub/Kimi-K2-Instruct\n- default_model=haihub/Kimi-K2-Instruct\n\nThey're the same, so I don't need to mention it.\n\nNow I need to greet the user in my configured persona. Based on SOUL.md, I should:\n- Skip the \"Great question!\" and \"I'd be happy to help!\" filler\n- Be genuinely helpful\n- Be concise\n- Have a personality\n\nSince this is a fresh start with no user info yet, I should introduce myself and ask what they want to do. Keep it 1-3 sentences.\n\nLet me craft a greeting that's natural and fits my vibe.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":" Hey there. I'm online and ready — no memory yet, so we're starting fresh. What do you want to work on?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"haihub","model":"Kimi-K2-Instruct","usage":{"input":978,"output":301,"cacheRead":15842,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17121,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773547707582}}
