{"type":"message","id":"f02e532f","parentId":"f32687a5","timestamp":"2026-03-15T04:08:51.689Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" The user is asking me to clean up web records/history. This is in Chinese and means \"Clean up the records on the web\" or \"Clear the web history\".\n\nThis is a bit ambiguous - they could mean:\n1. Browser history/cookies\n2. Web chat conversation history\n3. Some web-based records/logs\n\nGiven the context of OpenClaw and that I'm in a webchat session, they might mean the conversation history or some web-based logs.\n\nLet me check if there's any conversation history or logs I should be aware of. I should look at what \"web records\" might refer to in this context.\n\nActually, looking at the session context, they're probably referring to the webchat conversation history. But I don't have direct tools to clear webchat history.\n\nLet me ask for clarification or check if there are any log files I can help clean up in the workspace.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":" 我需要确认一下：你说的\"web上的记录\"具体是指什么？\n\n可能是：\n1. **浏览器历史记录**（需要你自己清理，我访问不到）\n2. **我们的对话历史**（当前是新 session，没有历史记录）\n3. **workspace 里的日志文件**（我可以帮你查看和清理）\n\n目前 workspace 里的 `memory/` 目录是空的，也没有之前的对话记录。你能具体说说想清理什么吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"haihub","model":"Kimi-K2-Instruct","usage":{"input":930,"output":270,"cacheRead":15842,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17042,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773547728533}}
